text:
Events:
debug - {user: <user object to send message to>}
sslacky <user> doesn't have <role> role - Removes a role from a user
sslacky <user> has <role> role - Assigns a role to a user
sslacky <user> is a badass guitarist - assign a role to a user
sslacky <user> is not a badass guitarist - remove a role from a user
sslacky animate me <query> - The same thing as `image me`, except adds a few parameters to try to return an animated GIF instead.
sslacky die - End sslacky process
sslacky echo <text> - Reply back with <text>
sslacky fake event <event> - Triggers the <event> event for debugging reasons
sslacky help - Displays all of the help commands that sslacky knows about.
sslacky help <query> - Displays all help commands that match <query>.
sslacky image me <query> - The Original. Queries Google Images for <query> and returns a random top result.
sslacky map me <query> - Returns a map view of the area returned by `query`.
sslacky mustache me <query> - Searches Google Images for the specified query and mustaches it.
sslacky mustache me <url> - Adds a mustache to the specified URL.
sslacky ping - Reply with pong
sslacky pug bomb N - get N pugs
sslacky pug me - Receive a pug
sslacky show storage - Display the contents that are persisted in the brain
sslacky show users - Display all users that sslacky knows about
sslacky the rules - Make sure sslacky still knows the rules.
sslacky time - Reply with current time
sslacky translate me <phrase> - Searches for a translation for the <phrase> and then prints that bad boy out.
sslacky translate me from <source> into <target> <phrase> - Translates <phrase> from <source> into <target>. Both <source> and <target> are optional
sslacky what role does <user> have - Find out what roles are assigned to a specific user
sslacky who has admin role - Find out who's an admin and can assign roles
sslacky who is <user> - see what roles a user has
sslacky youtube me <query> - Searches YouTube for the query and returns the video embed link.
ship it - Display a motivation squirrel
